WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en-GB

00:00:09.370 --> 00:00:15.170
We'd like to welcome you to Caalm Camp, our
family-run rural retreat in the heart of the

00:00:15.170 --> 00:00:20.390
scenic Dorset countryside. We have taken the
very best things about camping in the South

00:00:20.390 --> 00:00:26.630
West of England and added comfortable beds
with fresh white linen sheets in our beautiful,

00:00:26.630 --> 00:00:32.099
authentic hand-painted Yurts from Mongolia.
We are open year round and our fully insulated

00:00:32.099 --> 00:00:38.260
Yurts, individual wood/coal burning stoves
and communal room ensures a warm, dry holiday

00:00:38.260 --> 00:00:44.120
no matter what the weather outside!

00:00:44.120 --> 00:00:49.860
We have six traditional Mongolian yurts available
to rent, situated in a peaceful field on our

00:00:49.860 --> 00:00:56.059
former Dairy Farm. Each yurt is brightly painted
in the authentic Mongolian style. Inside they

00:00:56.059 --> 00:01:00.800
are beautifully equipped and furnished and
sleep up to six. (we also have Travel cots

00:01:00.800 --> 00:01:06.480
available on request). Each yurt also has
lighting and electricity for recharging your

00:01:06.480 --> 00:01:09.970
gadgets, and induction hob for your morning
coffee or tea . Towels and linens are included

00:01:09.970 --> 00:01:13.140
in your freshly made up yurt when you arrive.
For an extra level of comfort, we also have

00:01:13.140 --> 00:01:24.250
a holiday cottage that sleeps four people.
call us to check availability.

00:01:24.250 --> 00:01:29.870
We pride ourselves on the fact that our facilities
far exceed most other Glamping sites, with

00:01:29.870 --> 00:01:35.260
each yurt, you will have your own secure luxury
private shower room, and use of a fully equipped

00:01:35.260 --> 00:01:40.930
kitchen complete with an individual fridge,
cutlery, crockery and cooking utensils for

00:01:40.930 --> 00:01:46.940
each yurt, perfect for preparing a picnic
or cooking a hearty farmhouse breakfast!

00:01:46.940 --> 00:01:51.850
Our yurts even come with WiFi! We have pool
and table tennis on site as well as board

00:01:51.850 --> 00:01:55.410
games for the family.
Whether you are booking a romantic break,

00:01:55.410 --> 00:02:03.620
a family camping holiday or a friends reunion,
Caalm Camp in Dorset is just the place!

00:02:03.620 --> 00:02:10.330
Lie back and look up at the stars while you
toast your toes in front of your woodburning

00:02:10.330 --> 00:02:15.950
stove, or gather with friends or family to
enjoy a barbecue in your own outdoor seating

00:02:15.950 --> 00:02:18.569
area.
We have a tranquil lake on the property which

00:02:18.569 --> 00:02:24.299
is perfect for early morning meditation, picnics,
or just watching the sun glimmer over its

00:02:24.299 --> 00:02:28.689
surface as it sets!
Children can scramble about on our wooden

00:02:28.689 --> 00:02:34.360
play equipment and you can relax knowing the
area is securely fenced in and safe.

00:02:34.360 --> 00:02:39.540
Children can also get closer to the wildlife,
whether it be our own kid friendly goats,

00:02:39.540 --> 00:02:46.730
docile cows, cocky Rooster, hens or our visiting
wild deer, rabbits and pheasants.

00:02:46.730 --> 00:02:52.480
If you are in need of extra pampering, we
can even provide you with your own relaxing

00:02:52.480 --> 00:02:57.819
therapy treatment .

00:02:57.819 --> 00:03:03.780
Our location is convenient to myriad attractions
from nearby Shaftesbury for it wonderful shopping,

00:03:03.780 --> 00:03:09.260
dining, open air markets and entertainment
to the lovely Sturminster Newton with its

00:03:09.260 --> 00:03:14.879
famous Old Mill Museum and Cycle Path.
We have Todber Manor Fisheries directly next

00:03:14.879 --> 00:03:19.939
door, with well stocked ponds for the avid
angler, to the gourmet Udder Farm Shop which

00:03:19.939 --> 00:03:25.569
stock all locally grown items; with everything
from fresh fruit and vegetables to meats and

00:03:25.569 --> 00:03:31.499
poultry to locally produced wines and ales;
all to make your camping experience truly

00:03:31.499 --> 00:03:35.650
first class.
Close by, there are a selection of beautiful

00:03:35.650 --> 00:03:40.969
pubs from The Mitre in Shaftesbury, The Kings
Arms with its much talked about Sunday Roasts,

00:03:40.969 --> 00:03:45.390
or the Salt Cellar restaurant overlooking
the famous Gold Hill.

00:03:45.390 --> 00:03:50.319
Whether you want a relaxing holiday lazing
about or to use us as a base for exploring

00:03:50.319 --> 00:03:55.790
Dorset, Somerset and Wiltshire, you'll find
Caalm Camp offers the perfect way to unwind

00:03:55.790 --> 00:04:01.109
at the end of each day; watching the sun go
down as you toast marshmallows round the fire

00:04:01.109 --> 00:04:06.540
pit before retiring to your yurt for a cosy
and comfortable night's sleep.

00:04:06.540 --> 00:04:12.190
We're open all year round for long weekends,
mid-week breaks or full week-long glamping

00:04:12.190 --> 00:04:17.760
holidays; have a look round our website, especially
the wider area section of our website for

00:04:17.760 --> 00:04:23.020
more local attractions! and don't hesitate
to call us if you have any queries.

00:04:23.020 --> 00:04:27.600
Check us out on TripAdvisor, and read the
experiences of guests that have stayed at

00:04:27.600 --> 00:04:28.720
Caalm Camp.

00:04:28.720 --> 00:04:33.690
Keep calm and carry on camping all year round,
..at Caalm Camp!!

